title: IQM Quantum Computers - Wikipedia
snippet: IQM Quantum Computers is a Finnish quantum computing hardware and software company headquartered in Espoo, Finland. [1][2][3] The company develops and commercializes quantum computers based on superconducting technology.

title: Brand new unicorn IQM sets its sights beyond Europe for its quantum ...
